I.  This course works with DDI/Innovus 
    25.1 RTM

II.  Disk Space requirements: 2G including data and output
     files.

III. Software products required for the course:
      Digital Design and Implementation which includes Innovus Implementation System

IV. Testing the course installation:
    To test the software and course installation execute the test
    script file. cd to the FPR directory and execute the .testscript

V. OS Requirement
   To run DDI 25.1, and from this release onwards RH8.4 is the minimum requirement and won't run on RH7.X.



